    "body": "This PR is based on #28155 and adds unit test coverage for each change in it (i.e. tests that fail on master), as well as missing unit test coverage in general for `CConnman::AddNode(), ConnectNode(), GetAddedNodeInfo(), and AlreadyConnectedToAddress()`. I'm building on these initial unit tests for writing coverage for #28248.\r\n\r\nA version of this branch based on current master rather than that PR is [here](https://github.com/jonatack/bitcoin/commits/2023-10-net_peer_connection_tests-for-master).\r\n\r\nSuggest the following for running the tests locally:\r\n\r\n```\r\n./src/test/test_bitcoin -t net_peer_connection_tests -l all -- -printtoconsole=1 \r\n```\r\nor\r\n```\r\n./src/test/test_bitcoin -t net_peer_connection_tests -l message -- -printtoconsole=1\r\n```\r\n",
